Digital Deities - The enlightened one

"Under the tree, he realized, it wasn't the outside he wanted to control. It was the inside." - AJ

This piece was inspired by change. 

About The 50/50Project
Started by mother/son artist duo AJ, the goal of the project was to create meaningful and thought-provoking art with a mission. A mission to make NFTs a change catalyst for the good of society. 50% of all proceeds go to selected NGOs from TheGivingBlock.com. 

The 5050Project also denotes that each item is made 50% by hand (by A) and 50% with CGI (by J) - making every piece unique even before it is minted.

Things to note:
1. Please be kind to us and other artists here
2. Each item will always be priced at 1 ETH
3. Proof of donation will be shared as a gasless NFT item within 7 days
4. All copyrights will be owned by the purchaser after-sale
5. New collections every 1st Sunday of the month
